uti's%20governance%20over%20the%20past%20two-and-a-half%20years.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20completion%20of%20two-and-a-half%20years.%20The%20work%20done%20by%20our%20government--the%20MahaYuti%20government--by%20the%20three%20of%20us%20and%20our%20team%20in%20the%20last%202.5%20years%20is%20remarkable.%20It%20will%20be%20written%20in%20golden%20letters%20in%20history.%20We%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20taken%20such%20significant%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Shinde.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMumbai's%20Azad%20Maidan%20has%20been%20transformed%20into%20a%20fortified%20zone%20for%20the%20event.%20Over%204%2C000%20police%20personnel%2C%20including%20specialised%20units%20like%20the%20State%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(SRPF)%2C%20Quick%20Response%20Teams%20(QRT)%2C%20and%20bomb%20disposal%20squads%2C%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20attendees.%20Traffic%20in%20South%20Mumbai%20is%20being%20managed%20by%20280%20personnel%20from%20the%20traffic%20wing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ceremony%20is%20expected%20to%20draw%20an%20audience%20of%2042%2C000%2C%20with%20seating%20arrangements%20for%202%2C000%20VIPs%2C%20including%20religious%20leaders%20and%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733379840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fjhcg823g_e-shinde-fadnavis-ajit-pawar-_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-maharashtra-oath-ceremony-today-over-40-000-expected-to-attend-10-points-7175571%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20leader%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20will%20take%20oath%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20for%20the%20third%20time%20today.%20The%20event%20in%20Mumbai%20will%20also%20see%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20NCP's%20Ajit%20Pawar%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20in%20the%20newly%20formed%20cabinet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2