2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Beginning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20born%20in%20a%20Marathi%20Brahmin%20family%20in%20Nagpur%20to%20Gangadhar%20Fadnavis%20and%20Sarita%20Fadnavis.%20His%20father%20was%20with%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%20and%20then%20the%20BJP%20and%20rose%20to%20become%20a%20member%20of%20the%20state%20legislative%20council.%20According%20to%20his%20website%2C%20young%20Devendra%20was%20put%20in%20Indira%20Convent%20School%2C%20Nagpur%2C%20but%20he%20refused%20to%20study%20there%20after%20his%20father%20was%20arrested%20during%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government.%20He%20was%20then%20put%20in%20Saraswati%20Vidyalaya%2C%20run%20by%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20parent%20RSS.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20graduated%20in%20law%20with%20a%20gold%20medal%20before%20completing%20an%20MBA.%20His%20political%20journey%20continued%20alongside%2C%20from%20the%20Nagpur%20civic%20body%20to%20the%20state%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Flljkjdug_fadnavis-modi_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Big%20Break%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20after%20he%20became%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20chief%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20led%20the%20party%20to%20a%20massive%20score%20of%20122%20seats%20in%20the%202014%20state%20polls.%20Riding%20high%20on%20the%20wave%20in%20favour%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20crossed%20the%20100-seat%20mark%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20formed%20a%20government%20in%20alliance%20with%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Over%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20he%20spearheaded%20several%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20Mumbai%20coastal%20road%20plan%20and%20Nagpur%20Metro%2C%20earning%20popularity%20among%20urban%20voters.%20His%20political%20acumen%20and%20development%20outlook%20earned%20him%20the%20praise%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20called%20him%20%26quot%3BNagpur's%20gift%20to%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20completed%20his%20first%20term%2C%20he%20became%20only%20the%20second%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Vasantrao%20Naik%20in%20the%201970s%20to%20complete%20a%20full%20term%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Setback%2C%20And%20The%20Sacrifice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20fought%20the%202019%20state%20polls%20in%20an%20alliance%20and%20scored%20the%20numbers%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20But%20differences%20arose%20over%20the%20top%20post%2C%20with%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20insisting%20on%20rotational%20Chief%20ministership.%20Eventually%2C%20Sena%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20alliance.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20tied%20up%20with%20NCP's%20Ajit%20Pawar%20to%20cobble%20up%20the%20numbers%20and%20took%20the%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20a%20hurried%20ceremony.%20But%20this%20government%20lasted%20four%20days.%20The%20Sena%20then%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20NCP%20and%20Congress%20with%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20became%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20waited%20for%20the%20right%20time.%20This%20time%20came%20in%202022%20when%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20aide%20Eknath%20Shinde%20led%20a%20mutiny%20that%20split%20the%20Sena.%20The%20Shinde%20Sena%20decided%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%20And%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20faced%20a%20tough%20test%20of%20loyalty.%20Despite%20the%20BJP%20holding%20more%20numbers%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20the%20party%20leadership%20agreed%20to%20let%20Mr%20Shinde%20become%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20accepted%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20role%2C%20although%20reluctantly.%20This%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20decision%2C%20for%20a%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20be%20Number%202%20despite%20his%20party%20holding%20the%20maximum%20MLAs.%20But%20this%20decision%20established%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20party's%20loyal%20soldier%20ready%20to%20make%20sacrifices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ft5fc4pm_devendra-fadnavis_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Return%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20suffered%20a%20big%20setback%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20this%20year%2C%20few%20would%20have%20imagined%20how%20much%20the%20picture%20would%20change%20months%20later.%20The%202024%20state%20polls%20saw%20the%20BJP%20post%20its%20best-ever%20score%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20winning%20132%20out%20of%20148%20seats%20it%20contested.%20The%20Mahayuti's%20tally%20reached%20230%20in%20the%20288-member%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20government%20formation%20is%20always%20a%20tall%20task%20when%20multiple%20allies%20are%20involved.%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Sena%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20and%20argued%20that%20the%20election%20was%20won%20under%20his%20leadership.%20But%20the%20BJP%20put%20its%20foot%20down%20and%20the%20legislators%20rallied%20behind%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20citing%20how%20he%20took%20a%20backseat%20in%202022%20and%20the%20need%20to%20reward%20him%20for%20leading%20the%20party%20to%20the%20mammoth%20mandate.%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20had%20once%20said%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmodern%20Abhimanyu%26quot%3B%20who%20knows%20how%20to%20break%20the%20Ch