ia-make-one-major-change-7176012%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Prince%20Harry%20Said%20On%20Separation%20Rumours%20With%20Meghan%20Markle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20whenever%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20Meghan%20Markle%20made%20solo%20public%20appearances%2C%20the%20media%20and%20royal%20family%20observers%20wondered%20if%20there%20was%20trouble%20in%20their%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20Prince%20Harry%20has%20finally%20addressed%20all%20the%20rumours%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CApparently%20we've%20bought%20or%20moved%20houses%2010%2C%2012%20times.%20We've%20apparently%20divorced%20maybe%2010%2C%2012%20times%20as%20well.%20So%20it's%20just%20like%2C%20what%3F%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20The%20New%20York%20Times'%202024%20DealBook%20Summit%20in%20New%20York%20City%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Harry%2C%2040%2C%20discussed%20his%20life%20and%20speculations%20surrounding%20his%20marriage%20with%20Meghan%2C%2043.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20the%20Summit%2C%20DealBook%20founder%20Andrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%20asked%20Harry%20about%20the%20interest%20many%20have%20in%20the%20couple's%20personal%20life.%20He%20shared%20that%20when%20he%20searched%20his%20name%20on%20Google%20News%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20people%20fascinated%20by%20everything%20you're%20doing%2C%20all%20the%20time.%20They're%20fascinated%20by%20Meghan%20being%20in%20California%20right%20now%2C%20and%20you're%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sorkin%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAsked%20why%20the%20couple%20was%20doing%20independent%20events%20and%20not%20together%2C%20Harry%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBecause%20you%20invited%20me%2C%20you%20should%20have%20known!%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSorkin%20then%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BTrue...%20Is%20that%20normal%20for%20you%3F%20The%20second%20there's%20an%20article%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20in%20California%2C%20you're%20in%20New%20York%20%E2%80%94%20they%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98Well%2C%20what%20is%20happening%20with%20these%20two%2C%20right%3F'%20Is%20that%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20you%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20that%20there's%20so%20much%20interest%20in%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20this%2C%20Harry%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20that's%20definitely%20not%20a%20good%20thing.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAlthough%20Harry%20admitted%20that%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20keep%20up%20with%2C%20he%20tries%20to%20ignore%20it.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CIt's%20hard%20to%20keep%20up%20with%2C%20but%20that's%20why%20you%20just%20sort%20of%20ignore%20it.%20The%20people%20I%20feel%20most%20sorry%20about%20are%20the%20trolls...Their%20hopes%20are%20just%20built%20and%20built%2C%20and%20it's%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Yes%2C%20yes%2C%20yes%2C'%20and%20then%20it%20doesn't%20happen.%20So%20I%20feel%20sorry%20for%20them.%20Genuinely%2C%20I%20do.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20further%20said%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20doubt%E2%80%9D%20that%20his%20interview%20with%20Sorkin%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20spun%20or%20twisted%20somehow%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20maybe%20%26quot%3Bthe%20host%20will%20also%20be%20trolled%20relentlessly.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CFor%20that%2C%20I%20can%20only%20apologise%2C%20but%20you%20did%20invite%20me%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20my%20fault%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20quipped.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20divorce%20rumours%20started%20when%20the%20Duke%20and%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20were%20seen%20appearing%20separately%20at%20various%20professional%20engagements.%20While%20many%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprofessional%20separation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20move%20was%20said%20to%20be%20a%20new%20%E2%80%9Ctwin-track%E2%80%9D%20approach%20that%20could%20overhaul%20their%20image%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F12%2F04%2Fentertainment%2Fprince-harry-breaks-silence-on-meghan-markle-divorce-rumors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bla