rat%20steers%20popular%20brands%20like%20Coach%2C%20Kate%20Spade%2C%20and%20Stuart%20Weitzman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2024%2F12%2F04%2Ftapestry-ceo-joanne-crevoiserat-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Fortune's%20%26quot%3BLeadership%20Next%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Crevoiserat%20gave%20host%20Diane%20Brady%20her%20leadership%2C%20business%2C%20and%20career%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20nuggets%20of%20wisdom%20from%20the%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee97af9c-375f-4bb9-8e69-cb6222fa6909%5C%22%3E1.%20Have%20'insatiable%20curiosity'%20about%20the%20customer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrevoiserat's%20first%20top%20was%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Binsatiable%20curiosity%20about%20the%20consumer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20understanding%20the%20customer%20goes%20beyond%20survey%20data%20and%20involves%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20a%20step%20deeper%20into%20the%20consumer's%20closet%2C%20into%20their%20home%2C%20and%20talking%20to%20them%20about%20what%20matters%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20this%20ensures%20that%20the%20brand%20can%20build%20more%20relevant%20products%20and%20experiences%20for%20their%20consumers%2C%20she%20told%20Fortune.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2271eae5ff-f660-49ec-994f-03654393bd82%5C%22%3E2.%20Don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20take%20side%20steps%20in%20your%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20second%20piece%20of%20advice%20was%20to%20enjoy%20the%20career%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRelationship%20building%2C%20understanding%20the%20end-to-end%20business%20is%20not%20always%20the%20intended%20outcome%20of%20a%20specific%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Crevoiserat%20said%20to%20Fortune.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20on%20your%20job%20responsibility%20list%2C%20but%20it%20helps%20you%20build%20your%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20careers%20aren't%20always%20going%20to%20be%20linear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrevoiserat%20has%20held%20top%20jobs%20in%20several%20retail%20companies%2C%20including%20Walmart%2C%20Kohl's%2C%20and%20Abercrombie%20%26amp%3B%20Fitch.%20She%20became%20Tapestry's%20CEO%20in%202020%20after%20working%20as%20the%20company's%20finance%20chief%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20taken%20a%20few%20side%20steps%20in%20my%20career%20and%20people%20have%20said%2C%20'Trust%20me%20on%20this%2C'%20and%20you%20have%20to%20have%20a%20little%20trust.%20But%20it%20has%20worked%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Crevoiserat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20do%20see%20the%20benefit%20of%20taking%20those%20side%20steps%20and%20being%20able%20to%20have%20a%20bigger%20picture%20and%20better%20perspective%20on%20business%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b73d0ef-5f17-4229-a313-ef2abeb14894%5C%22%3E3.%20Inspiration%20strikes%20outside%20the%20office%20walls%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrevoiserat%20said%20that%20being%20%26quot%3Boutdoors%20and%20moving%26quot%3B%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20inspiration%20from%20being%20in%20the%20natural%20world%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20a%20walk%20along%20the%20Hudson%20or%20a%20hike%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20staying%20inside%20a%20building%20all%20day%20makes%20it%20%26quot%3Bhard%20to%20be%20inspired%20if%20all%20you're%20seeing%20are%20the%20same%20four%20walls%20over%20and%20over%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20draws%20inspiration%20and%20energy%20from%20walking%2C%20running%2C%20hiking%2C%20and%20visiting%20museums%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Crevoiserat%20and%20Brady%20also%20discussed%20the%20potential%20impact%20of%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20proposed%20tariffs%20on%20foreign%20imports%20and%20Tapestry's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fversace-parent-stock-plu