-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20Kapil%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20that%20Kambli%20must%20be%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKapil%20(Dev%2C%20captain%20of%20the%201983%20team)%20has%20told%20me%20clearly%20that%20if%20he%20wants%20to%20go%20to%20rehab%2C%20then%20we%20are%20willing%20to%20help%20him%20financially%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20India%20fast%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Balwinder%20Singh%20Sandhu%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59659-balwinder-singh-sandhu-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBalwinder%20Singh%20Sandhu%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20he%20has%20to%20check%20into%20rehab%20himself%20first.%20Only%20if%20he%20does%20that%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20foot%20the%20bill%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20long%20the%20treatment%20lasts%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandhu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidered%20two%20of%20the%20finest%20cricketing%20talents%20in%20the%20country%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Vinod%20Kambli%20began%20their%20cricketing%20journeys%20on%20a%20promising%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20stitched%20a%20famous%20partnership%20of%20664%20runs%20for%20their%20school%2C%20Shardashram%20Vidyamandir%2C%20in%20a%20Harris%20Shield%20match%20while%20also%20registering%20unbeaten%20triple%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20went%20on%20to%20represent%20India%20at%20the%20highest%20level%2C%20though%20Kambli's%20career%20went%20downhill%20quickly%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20disciplinary%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733373120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fateumbs_cs_625x300_05_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgone-to-rehab-14-times-vinod-kamblis-health-issues-revealed-by-close-friend-7175793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vinod%20Kambli's%20recent%20public%20appearance%20at%20a%20memorial%20event%20for%20legendary%20coach%20Ramakant%20Achrekar%20has%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20fans%20concerned%20about%20his%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgone-to-rehab-14-times-vinod-kamblis-health-issues-revealed-by-close-friend-7175793%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Renaissance%20Of%20Notre-Dame%20Cathedral%3A%20Miracles%20And%20Controversies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20than%20five-year%20reconstruction%20of%20Notre%20Dame%20cathedral%20has%20featured%20some%20near-miraculous%20recoveries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20controversies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20official%20reopening%20of%20the%20cathedral%20on%20Saturday%2C%20AFP%20looks%20at%20some%20of%20the%20key%20moments%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20saviours%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParis%20firefighters%20won%20universal%20praise%20for%20their%20swift%20and%20decisive%20action%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20April%2015%2C%202019%2C%20with%20officers%20later%20saying%20they%20thought%20they%20were%20only%2030%20minutes%20away%20from%20seeing%20the%20structure%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBattling%20smoke%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20falling%20debris%2C%20they%20formed%20a%20human%20chain%20with%20church%20officials%20to%20evacuate%20the%20most%20precious%20artifacts%20and%20religious%20treasures%2C%20helping%20preserve%20most%20of%20the%20cathedral's%20irreplaceable%20contents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%20saw%20divine%20intervention%20in%20how%20a%20copper%20statue%20of%20a%20rooster%20that%20had%20sat%20atop%20the%20building's%20incinerated%2019th-century%20spire%20was%20found%20afterwards%20intact%20amid%20the%20scorched%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20contents%20--%20three%20relics%2C%20including%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20the%20Crown%20of%20Thorns%20supposedly%20worn%20by%20Jesus%20before%20his%20crucifixion%20--%20also%20survived%2C%20with%20the%20battered%20rooster%20now%20on%20display%20in%20a%20Paris%20museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20cathedral%2C%20images%20the%20day%20after%20the%20blaze%20revealed%20that%20a%20giant%20gold%20cross%20on%20the%20altar%20was%20still%20standing%20amid%20the%20still%20smouldering%20wreckage%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20hope%20and%20defiance%20for%20many%20on%20a%20dark%20day%20for%20Christians%20and%20the%20country%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContested%20design%20contest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20called%20the%20fire%20%26quot%3Ban%20opportunity%20to%20come%20together%26quot%3B%20but%20any%20sense%20of%20national%20unity%20after%20the%20disaster%20quickly%20broke%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20suggestion%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Belement%20of%20modern%20architecture%26quot%3B%20be%20included%20in%20the%20rebuild%20drew%20immediate%20criticism%20from%20conservatives%20who%20demanded%20that%20the%20reconstruction%20be%20faithful%20to%20the%20last%20major%20update%20by%20architect%20Eugene%20Viollet-le-Duc%20in%201844.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20general%20put%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20rebuild%20publicly%20fell%20out%20with%20the%20lead%20architect%20over%20the%20redesign%2C%20while%20entries%20for%20an%20architectural%20competition%20to%20select%20a%20new%20spire%20resulted%20in%20lurid%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20suggestion%20shown%20by%20First%20Lady%20Brigitte%20Macron%20to%20then-culture%20minister%20Roselyne%20Bachelot%20resembled%20a%20%26quot%3Bphallus%20with%20its%20base%20surrounded%20with%20golden%20balls%2C%26quot%3B%20Bachelot%20wrote%20in%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20old%20spire%20was%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20new%20stained%20glass%20windows%20are%20set%20to%20be%20installed%20featuring%20work%20by%20contemporary%20artists%20--%20a%20modest%20nod%20to%20modernity%20and%20Macron's%20original%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELead%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotre%20Dame's%20roof%20and%20spire%20were%20covered%20by%20around%20400%20tonnes%20of%20lead%2C%20a%20toxic%20heavy%20metal%20that%20melted%20and%20vaporised%20with%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20fire%2C%20with%20some%20of%20it%20thought%20to%20have%20polluted%20the%20surrounding%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20cleaned%20nearby%20schools%20and%20advised%20local%20residents%20to%20wipe%20surfaces%20in%20their%20homes%20because%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20poisoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20health%20charity%20joined%20forces%20with%20a%20union%20and%20parents%20of%20local%20schoolchildren%20to%20lodge%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20in%202022%20that%20accused%20authorities%20of%20failing%20to%20take%20every%20precaution%20to%20prevent%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharges%20are%20possible%20if%20authorities%20or%20contractors%20are%20found%20to%20have%20been%20negligent%20in%20protecting%20the%20health%20of%20residents%20or%20workers%20sent%20in%20to%20decontaminate%20the%20site%2C%20with%20an%20investigating%20magistrate%20overseeing%20a%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECause%20unknown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20Paris%20prosecutor%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20fire%2C%20Remy%20Heitz%2C%20said%20shortly%20after%20the%20inferno%20that%20he%20believed%20that%20an%20accident%20such%20as%20an%20electrical%20fault%20or%20a%20cigarette%20butt%20was%20the%20most%20likely%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20workers%20renovating%20the%20roof%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20fire%20were%20known%20to%20have%20smoked%20on%20site%2C%20but%20investigators%20have%20never%20been%20able%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20exact%20starting%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20about%20an%20arson%20attack%20has%20been%20investigated%20during%20five%20years%20of%20forensic%20analysis%2C%20but%20no%20evidence%20was%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20chief%20Paris%20prosecutor%20Laure%20Beccuau%20said%20in%20April%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20closer%20we%20have%20got%20to%20the%20spot%20the%20fire%20started%2C%20and%20the%20more%20results%20of%20analyses%20come%20back%2C%20the%20more%20weight%20is%20lent%20to%20the%20theory%20of%20an%20accident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFee%20row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECulture%20Minister%20Rachida%20Dati%20has%20proposed%20that%20visitors%20to%20the%20restored%20cathedral%20pay%20a%20five-euro%20(%245.25)%20entry%20ticket%2C%20with%20the%20funds%20set%20to%20be%20routed%20to%20some%204%2C000%20churches%20in%20need%20of%20repairs%20around%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharging%20for%20entry%20--%20entering%20Notre%20Dame%20was%20previously%20free%20--%20would%20bring%20the%20tourist%20attraction%20into%20line%20with%20St%20Paul's%20cathedral%20in%20London%20or%20Milan's%20Duomo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20senior%20French%20church%20leaders%20have%20criticised%20the%20idea%2C%20with%20a%20senior%20bishop%20saying%20churches%20and%20cathedrals%20had%20%26quot%3Balways%20been%20places%20open%20to%20all%26quot%3B%20and%20making%20money%20from%20visitors%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetrayal%20of%20their%20original%20vocation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20state%20owns%20Notre%20Dame%20and%20has%20the%20final%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733373060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fhs69unro_notredame-de-_625x300_05_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthe-renaissance-of-notre-dame-cathedral-miracles-and-controversies-7175934%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A