orities-in-bangladesh-124120500174_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Male%20Cheetahs%20Released%20Into%20Open%20Wild%20Areas%20At%20Kuno%20National%20Park%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20International%20Cheetah%20Day%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20two%20male%20cheetahs%20Agni%20and%20Vayu%20were%20released%20into%20an%20open%20wild%20area%20at%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20(KNP)%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMale%20cheetahs%20were%20released%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20senior%20wildlife%20officials%20associated%20with%20Kuno%20ensuring%20that%20all%20logistical%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20security%20measures%20were%20in%20place%20to%20facilitate%20the%20smooth%20transition%20of%20Agni%20and%20Vayu%20into%20their%20new%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kuno%20officials%2C%20the%20preparation%20for%20releasing%20cheetahs%20Agni%20and%20Vayu%20started%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20The%20Cheetah%20steering%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20Chairman%20Rajesh%20Gopal%2C%20visited%20Kuno%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20review%20the%20final%20preparations%20for%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheetahs%20Agni%20and%20Vayu%20were%20chosen%20for%20the%20open%20wild%20area%20because%20they%20were%20fit%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20new%20environment%20within%20Kuno.%20Officials%20said%20cheetahs%20were%20released%20into%20open%20wild%20areas%20marking%20the%20success%20of%20India's%20ambitious%20cheetah%20reintroduction%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20of%20Agni%20and%20Vayu%20will%20be%20closely%20monitored%20to%20ensure%20their%20safety%20and%20their%20capacity%20to%20adapt%20to%20a%20new%20environment.%20Officials%20said%20that%20Kuno%20National%20Park%20has%20been%20fully%20prepared%20to%20support%20the%20cheetahs%20in%20their%20new%20habitat%2C%20with%20the%20area%20secured%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20potential%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Forest%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20and%20