%2C%20U.S.%20investors%20resumed%20buying%20hand-over-fist%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joe%20McCann%2C%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20Asymmetric%2C%20a%20Miami%20digital%20assets%20hedge%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20strong%20debut%20for%20options%20on%20BlackRock's%20ETF%20in%20November%20with%20call%20options%20-%20bets%20on%20the%20price%20going%20up%20-%20substantially%20more%20popular%20than%20puts.%20McCann%20calculated%20the%20put%20to%20call%20ratio%20at%20about%2022%20to%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrypto-related%20stocks%20have%20soared%20along%20with%20the%20bitcoin%20price%2C%20with%20shares%20in%20bitcoin%20miner%20MARA%20Holdings%20up%20around%2065%25%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20rise%20is%20not%20without%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20industry%20was%20wracked%20by%20scandal%20with%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20FTX%20crypto%20exchange%20and%20the%20jailing%20of%20its%20founder%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cryptocurrency%20industry%20also%20has%20been%20criticized%20for%20its%20massive%20energy%20usage%2C%20while%20crypto%20crime%20remains%20a%20concern%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarket%20participants%20are%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20what%20happens%20now%20that%20bitcoin%20has%20broken%20above%20%24100%2C000%2C%20with%20investors%20and%20speculators%20possibly%20looking%20to%20pocket%20some%20of%20their%20recent%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20once%20we%20flush%20out%20those%20sell%20orders%2C%20this%20could%20go%20higher%20still%2C%20and%20very%20rapidly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steven%20McClurg%2C%20founder%20of%20Canary%20Capital%2C%20a%20digital%20assets%20investment%20firm.%20He%20said%20he%20expects%20bitcoin's%20price%20to%20hit%20%24120%2C000%20by%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%