%20pleasure%20in%20Spotify%20Wrapped%2C%20although%20I%20know%20it's%20a%20massively%20popular%20thing%20that%20many%20people%20%E2%80%94presumably%20those%20who%20don't%20listen%20to%20Raffi%20on%20repeat%20%E2%80%94%20really%20look%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20year%2C%20there's%20a%20new%20feature.%20And%20I%20struggle%20to%20imagine%20how%20anyone%20won't%20feel%20mildly%20weirded%20out%20by%20it%3A%20Spotify%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-notebooklm-audio-overviews-ai-podcast-tool-2024-01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20new%20NotebookLM%3C%2Fa%3E%20AI-powered%20feature%20to%20create%20an%20individualized%20AI-generated%20podcast%20with%20two%20talking%20heads%20discussing%20your%20listening%20habits%20in%20a%20conversational%2C%20podcast-y%20tone.%20Yikes!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20received%20a%203-minute%20podcast%20with%20a%20man%20and%20woman%20chatting%20about%20how%20impressive%20it%20was%20that%20I%20had%20listened%20to%20%26quot%3BCruel%20Summer%26quot%3B%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-disrupt-publishing-industry-eras-tour-book-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20my%204-year-old's%20current%20favorite%20tune%2C%20narrowly%20edging%20out%20%26quot%3BLet%20It%20Go%26quot%3B%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0so%20many%20times%20that%20I%20was%20in%20the%20Top%200.02%25%20of%20listeners.%20(I%20should%20note%20here%20that%20the%20podcast%20said%20I%20was%20in%20the%20Top%200.02%25%2C%20while%20the%20main%20Wrapped%20said%20it%20was%200.05%25.%20Possibly%20the%20podcast%20version%20hallucinated%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20understand%20why%20people%20like%20sharing%20screenshots%20from%20their%20Wrapped.%20It's%20normal%20to%20want%20to%20share%20what%20music%20you%20like%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20those%20lists%20say%20about%20you%20and%20your%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20listening%20to%20an%20AI%20podcast%20about%20it%3F%20Voiced%20by%20robots%3F%20I'm%20not%20sure%20anyone%20wants%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20NotebookLM%20is%20a%20fascinating%20product%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20played%20around%20with%20it%20a%20little%2C%20and%20it%20is%20very%20cool%2C%20if%20not%20uncanny.%20You%20can%20add%20in%20text%20or%20a%20PDF%20or%20other%20kinds%20of%20data%2C%20and%20it%20will%20create%20a%20conversational%20podcast%20episode%20with%20two%20hosts%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Blikes%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bums%26quot%3B%20and%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20got%20that%20factor%20about%20GenAI%20that%20makes%20you%20go%20%26quot%3Bwhoa%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20trying%20ChatGPT%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20have%20it%20write%20a%20poem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20got%20the%20dog-walking-on-its-hind-legs%20element%3A%20It's%20impressive%20because%20the%20dog%20can%20do%20it%20at%20all%2C%20not%20because%20it's%20doing%20it%20particularly%20well.%20The%20idea%20that%20AI%20could%20generate%20a%20chatty%20podcast%20that%20sounds%20almost%20real%20is%2C%20admittedly%2C%20mindblowing.%20But%20would%20you%20want%20to%20actually%20listen%20to%20it%3F%20I'm%20not%20really%20so%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20wondered%20what%20this%20would%20be%20used%20for%20%E2%80%94%20I%20assume%20some%20people%20find%20listening%20to%20something%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20engage%20with%20than%20simply%20reading%20it.%20You%20could%20take%20the%20Wikipedia%20page%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20War%20of%201812%2C%26quot%3B%20plug%20it%20into%20AI%2C%20and%20generate%20an%20engaging%20history%20podcast%20instead%20of%20slogging%20through%20dry%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20a%20business%20setting%2C%20perhaps%20a%20busy%20exec%20could%20upload%20an%20accounting%20report%20and%20listen%20to%20it%20while%20on%20the%20putting%20green%20instead%20of%20reading%20a%20stale%20PDF.%20(I%20tried%20uploading%20my%20tax%20return%20and%20created%20what%20may%20be%20the%20most%20boring%20pod