%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20OSB%20does%20manage%20to%20lend%20some%20bespoke%20detailing%20to%20the%20building%2C%20it%20is%20susceptible%20to%20moisture%20absorption.%20This%2C%20says%20Aameer%2C%20can%20affect%20its%20dimensional%20stability%20and%20performance%20over%20time.%20Another%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20since%20OSB%20is%20procured%20from%20trees%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cverify%20the%20specific%20environmental%20certifications%20and%20sustainability%20attributes%20of%20the%20OSB%20product%20being%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Compressed%20Stabilised%20Earth%20Bricks%20(CSEB)%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20study%20underscored%2C%20%E2%80%9CCompressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%20due%20to%20the%20lower%20amount%20of%20energy%20required%20for%20their%20production%2C%20lower%20cost%20and%20lower%20carbon%20footprint.%20Compared%20to%20cement%20concrete%2C%20CSEBs%20also%20require%20less%20embodied%20energy%2C%20with%20some%20authors%20indicating%20that%20only%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20production%20energy%20of%20cement%20concrete%20is%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20architects%20Rahul%20Kadri%2C%20Nithin%20Hosabettu%2C%20Sahil%20Bipin%20Deshpande%2C%20Viraj%20Naralkar%2C%20and%20Aakash%20Shrivastav%20of%20Mumbai-based%20IMK%20Architects%20were%20tasked%20with%20designing%20the%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%2C%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312182%2Fmaking-of-odisha-krushi-bhavan-sustainable-architecture-local-craftsmanship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20enthusiastic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20discovered%2C%20not%20only%20do%20the%20bricks%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20structure%20but%20they%20also%20boast%2080%20percent%20less%20energy%20consumption%20while%20achieving%20thermal%20comfort.%20The%20architects%20share%20that%20the%20bricks%20they%20used%20were%20made%20using%20a%20natural%20mix%20of%20red%20soil%2C%20sand%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(crumbled%20rock)%20stabilised%20with%20five%20percent%20cement.%20This%20ensured%20their%20durability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%20has%20been%20built%20with%20compressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20that%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386133%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%20has%20been%20built%20with%20compressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20that%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20IMK%20Architects%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20extend%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20scope%20of%20sustainability%2C%20the%20architects%20ensured%20that%20the%20bricks%20were%20made%20on-site%20by%20using%20a%20block-making%20machine%2C%20thus%20cutting%20the%20emission%20of%20carbon%2C%20while%20also%20employing%20local%20labour%20to%20sun%20dry%20instead%20of%20kiln-fire%20the%20bricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20all%20soils%20may%20be%20suitable%20for%20CSEB.%20Avoid%20using%20topsoil%20and%20organic%20soils.%20The%20type%20of%20stabiliser%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20mix%20will%20depend%20upon%20the%20soil%20in%20question.%20Cement%20works%20best%20for%20sandy%20soils%2C%20while%20lime%20works%20best%20for%20clayey%20soils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Acetylated%20wood%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWood%2C%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305212%2Feco-friendly-sustainable-house-in-thrissur-kerala-using-bamboo-bricks-wood-red-oxide-saves-electricity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstruction%20material%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20draws%20concerns%20for%20its%20responsiveness%20to%20environmental%20variables.%20So%2C%20imagine%20a%20variety%20of%20wood%20that%20performs%20well%20irrespective%20of%20the%20surroundings%3B%20one%20that%20can%20tolerate%20extreme%20temperatures%20as%20well%20as%20endure%20water%20exposure!%20When%20architect%20Vijay%20Dahiya%2C%20partner%20at%20team3%2C%20discovered%20acetylated%20wood%2C%20he%20was%20excited%20to%20try%20it%20out%20in%20one%20of%20his%20projects%2C%20%E2%80%98Mehra%20Residence%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mehra%20Residence%20in%20Delhi%20has%20been%20constructed%20using%20acetylated%20wood%20which%20lends%20anti-fungal%20properties%20to%20the%20structure%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vijay%20Dahiya%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386136%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Mehra%20Residence%20in%20Delhi%20has%20been%20constructed%20using%20acetylated%20wood%20which%20lends%20anti-fungal%20properties%20to%20the%20structure%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vijay%20Dahiya%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Aside%20from%20the%20initial%20cost%2C%20Vijay%20says%20there%20are%20only%20advantages%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20combined%20with%20water-based%2C%20low-VOC%20(volatile%20organic%20compounds)%20finishes%2C%20it%20maintains%20the%20eco-friendly%20integrity.%E2%80%9D%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20acetylation%20enhances%20the%20wood%E2%80%99s%20resistance%20against%20fungal%20decay%2C%20a%20study%20found.%20When%20the%20environmental%20impacts%20of%20acetylated%20Scots%20pine%2C%20tropical%20hardwood%20(Azobe)%2C%20and%20non-renewable%20materials%20(steel%2C%20concrete)%20were%20compared%2C%20the%20results%20showed%20that%20acetylated%20wood%20has%20a%20considerably%20lower%20carbon%20footprint%20than%20steel%2C%20concrete%20and%20unsustainably%20sourced%20Azobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Considering%20the%20material%20is%20wood%2C%20Vijay%20cautions%20that%20it%20should%20be%20sourced%20from%20sustainable%20forests.%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299507%2Feco-friendly-mud-red-stone-kerala-home-skylights-elliptical-windows-save-on-electric-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20carbon%20sequesters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20when%20used%20in%20construction%2C%20wood%20can%20further%20lock%20in%20that%20sequestered%20carbon%20for%20decades.%20If%20sourced%20from%20fast-growing%20species%20like%20spruce%20or%20pine%2C%20and%20sustainable%2C%20replenishable%20forests%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fijcsm.springeropen.com%2Farticles%2F10.1186%2Fs40069-022-00569-x%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUtilization%20of%20Solid%20Waste%20in%20the%20Production%20of%20Autoclaved%20Aerated%20Concrete%20and%20Their%20Effects%20on%20its%20Physio-mechanical%20and%20Microstructural%20Properties%3A%20Alternative%20Sources%2C%20Characterization%2C%20and%20Performance%20Insights%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20International%20Journal%20of%20Concrete%20Structures%20and%20Materials%2C%20Published%20on%208%20February%202023.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1364032124000467%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETowards%20the%20development%20of%20performance-efficient%20compressed%20earth%20blocks%20from%20industrial%20and%20agro-industrial%20by-products%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Science%20Direct%2C%20Published%20in%20April%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F307512746_ENVIRONMENTAL_IMPACT_OF_CONSTRUCTIONS_MADE_OF_ACETYLATED_WOOD%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnvironmental%20Impact%20of%20Constructions%20Made%20of%20Acetylated%20Wood%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Research%20Gate%2C%20Published%20in%20August%202016.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733322600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20wood%20tolerant%20to%20extreme%20temperatures%2C%20a%20paving%20material%20made%20of%20recycled%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20urban%20design%20is%20evolving!%20Let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20India%E2%80%99s%20sustainable%20architecture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386103%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-green-pavers-cseb-earth-blocks-orient-stranded-board%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20The%20APAAR%20Card%20Works%3A%20Answers%20to%20All%20Your%20Questions%20About%20This%20Student%20ID%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20and%20why%20was%20it%20introduced%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20introduced%20the%20Automated%20Permanent%20Academic%20Account%20Registry%20(APAAR%20ID)%2C%20aligned%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%20The%20initiative%20aims%20to%20simplify%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F383777%2Fsabia-share-book-india-children-literacy-education-government-schools-volunteer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacademic%20journey%20for%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20providing%20a%20digital%20identifier%20that%20links%20their%20educational%20records%20across%20multiple%20institutions%2C%20both%20within%20India%20and%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20type%20of%20academic%20information%20can%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20a%20unique%2012-digit%20code%20allowing%20students%20to%20digitally%20store%2C%20manage%2C%20and%20access%20a%20comprehensive%20range%20of%20academic%20information.%20This%20includes%20scorecards%2C%20marksheets%2C%20grade%20sheets%2C%20degrees%2C%20diplomas%2C%20certificates%2C%20and%20co-curricular%20achievements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20ensures%20smoother%20transitions%20between%20different%20educational%20stages%20and%20institutions%2C%20offering%20significant%20benefits%20for%20students%20pursuing%20education%20across%20various%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20access%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20or%20is%20there%20a%20specific%20process%20to%20follow%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAPAAR%20integrates%20with%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC)%2C%20enabling%20students%20to%20accumulate%2C%20transfer%2C%20and%20redeem%20credits%20across%20institutions.%20This%20system%20not%20only%20facilitates%20credit%20transfers%20but%20also%20tracks%20academic%20achievements%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363045%2Fgrassroots-organisations-initiatives-changemakers-teach-education-underprivileged-children-slum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanage%20their%20educational%20progress%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20students%20can%20access%20their%20academic%20records%20anytime%2C%20as%20it%20consolidates%20all%20their%20achievements%20onto%20a%20single%20platform%2C%20creating%20a%20comprehensive%20digital%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20requirements%20for%20applying%20for%20an%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20generating%20an%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20important%20prerequisites%20to%20consider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20UDISE%2B%20(Unified%20District%20Information%20System%20for%20Education%20Plus)%20records%20must%20match%20exactly%20with%20the%20name%20as%20per%20their%20Aadhaar.%20This%20ensures%20consistency%20and%20accuracy%20in%20the%20identification%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20Personal%20Education%20Number%20(PEN)%20is%20mandatory%20for%20generating%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20It%20is%20a%20unique%20identification%20number%20for%20students%20across%20all%20the%20education%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20APAAR%20ID%20only%20useful%20for%20current%20students%2C%20or%20can%20it%20benefit%20graduates%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20is%20beneficial%20not%20only%20for%20current%20students%20but%20also%20for%20graduates.%20For%20students%20like%20Krystelle%20Dsouza%2C%20a%20journalist%20pursuing%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20journalism%20at%20Mumbai%20University%2C%20this%20ID%20serves%20as%20a%20long-term%20academic%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20create%20my%20APAAR%20ID%20recently%2C%20and%20it%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC).%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20great%20step%20for%20students%20to%20have%20access%20to%20all%20of%20their%20degree%20certificates%20and%20anything%20they%E2%80%99ve%20accumulated%20throughout%20their%20academic%20trajectory%20in%20one%20place.%E2%80%9D%20This%20highlights%20how%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20helps%20graduates%20manage%20and%20access%20their%20academic%20records%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducational%20achievements%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20easily%20accessible%2C%20even%20after%20completing%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20I%20need%20to%20register%20for%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20and%20how%20do%20I%20get%20started%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20you%20have%20to%20register%20for%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20To%20register%2C%20visit%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website%20%E2%80%93%20abc.gov.in%20and%20click%20on%20%E2%80%98My%20Account%2C%E2%80%99%20then%20select%20the%20%E2%80