he%20indiscriminate%20blame%20or%20cause%20attributed%20to%20stubble%20burning%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20visible%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20notes%2C%20but%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CStubble%20burning%20only%20pollutes%20for%20two%20or%20three%20weeks%2C%20and%20its%20contribution%20to%20pollution%20throughout%20the%20year%20ranges%20from%200%20to%2030%20percent.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20is%20a%20major%20contributor%20and%20needs%20to%20stop%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20struggles%20with%20pollution%2C%20looking%20at%20cities%20that%20have%20successfully%20tackled%20the%20issue%20could%20provide%20solutions.%20Barcelona%2C%20which%20has%20greatly%20improved%20its%20air%20quality%2C%20offers%20valuable%20lessons%20for%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPedestrian-friendly%20%E2%80%98Superblocks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Europe%E2%80%99s%20most%20polluted%20cities%20throughout%20the%20late%2020th%20century%2C%20Barcelona%20has%20managed%20to%20reduce%20its%20air%20pollution%20with%20the%20help%20of%20progressive%20urban%20planning%2C%20transportation%20reforms%2C%20and%20green%20initiatives.%20In%202019%2C%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20mean%20annual%20PM%20particulate%20matter%20concentration%20was%2017%20%CE%BCg%2Fm%C2%B3%2C%20exceeding%20the%2010%20%CE%BCg%2Fm%C2%B3%20limit.%20Today%2C%20their%20real-time%20PM2.5%20level%20is%206%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%C2%B3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20city%20have%20lowered%20the%20levels%20of%20particulate%20matter%20and%20made%20it%20more%20livable%20and%20sustainable.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20strategies%20in%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20air%20pollution%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98superblock%E2%80%99%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20urban%20planning%20approach%20divides%20city%20streets%20in