en%20found%20stuck%20in%20the%20wires%2C%20injured%2C%20and%20because%20they%20are%20trapped%2C%20they%20are%20attacked%20by%20the%20feral%20dogs.%E2%80%9D%20This%20has%20led%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20injuries%20and%20deaths%2C%20further%20threatening%20the%20already%20vulnerable%20species.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20challenges%2C%20Sharvan%20and%20his%20team%20have%20started%20working%20on%20informing%20and%20sensitising%20people.%20Every%20time%20they%20get%20a%20call%20about%20an%20injured%20animal%2C%20they%20make%20sure%20to%20inform%20the%20people%20living%20in%20and%20around%20that%20part%20of%20the%20village.%20They%20show%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20animals%20that%20are%20harmed%20because%20of%20these%20wires%20to%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20farms.%20By%20letting%20them%20know%20the%20harsh%20consequences%20of%20their%20poorly%20thought-out%20actions%2C%20Sharvan%20makes%20sure%20to%20make%20them%20take%20responsibility.%20And%20it%20is%20but%20human%20nature%20to%20be%20considerate%20moving%20forth.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20the%20Orans%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20replenish%20the%20lands%2C%20their%20team%20has%20also%20uprooted%20invasive%20species%20of%20Julie%20flora%2C%20and%20planted%20native%20grasses%20to%20create%20grazing%20areas%20for%20the%20wildlife.%20They%20have%20focused%20on%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3Eber%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20Jujube)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhejri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejaal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Pilu%20Tree)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekumatiya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Acacia%20Senegal)%2C%20which%20are%20native%20to%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CChinkaras%20and%20blackbucks%20love%20%3Cem%3Eber%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20lot%2C%20so%20we%20plant%20those%20every%20year%20to%20replant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F